response.overview: New recorded material, brand new skits where Bjorn directed by some of Sweden's foremost comedians, such as Henry Schyffert and Robert Gustafsson! The DVD also contains Bjorn's appearance from the 2008 tour was completely sold out and a newly recorded interview. Of course, we also collected lots of Bjorn's already classic rock. In other words, a DVD that summarizes Bjorn's crazy year between 21 and 22. Includes everything you saw on Youtube and much more!
response.tagline: Our new comic star - Björn Gustafsson!
response.title: Björn Gustafsson: Ett livsverk
